https://youtu.be/MYHSGp_KH9o?si=uHqY1lmLlDNWV6SN

(1) update system with 'sudo pacman -Syu'

(2) enable multilib

> sudo nano /etc/pacman.conf

* release (#) on the following lines:

[multilib]
Include = /etc/pacman.d/mirrorlist

(3) update system with 'sudo pacman -Syu'

(4) install wine:
❯ sudo pacman -S wine winetricks wine-mono wine-gecko

(5) configure wine
> wine wincfg
